name: JGridstart
tagline: Friendly certificate management for end-users of grid computing infrastructures.
body:
### JGridstart
Get started with the grid easily. jGridstart helps grid end-users to request, obtain, install and renew grid certificates in a friendly way.

See http://wiki.nikhef.nl/grid/JGridstart
